column5: Thanks my twin brother from another mother!!!  Thanks everyone!
Happy belated birthday old man lol lets hook up soon
Just under the gun, Happy Birthday!! Hope it was a great one.
Thanks folks! Just like last year I guess... lol...
Happy Birthday Wayne - hope your day was a good one and all your wishes came true.  Tracker (Don)
Happy Birthday Wayne I hope you enjoy today as much as tomorrow.
Happy belated Wayne !!
Happy Bday Wayne I hope you get your wish.  Have a great day
Happy Birthday Wayne
Sorry I missed this somehow, Wayne. Hope you had a great day my friend.
Wayne ,hope yer day went well. I got you acouple of tree stands for your birthday.Where would ya like me to put them?     Be nice now.LOL
Happy Birthday Wayne I hope you get the best gift of them all.   Art
Happy Birthday Wayne
wisdom and glasses come with age....hope you seen a wise man in the mirror..  Cheers
Happy Belated Wayne may you have many more!!!!!   Sandro
And Big Cliff has the nerve to call me an old fart...seems I'm not the only one!  Welcome to the club and I hope you have a good one...LOL
Happy belated birthday Wayne,and many more. cheers !
Birthday, hell I'll drink to that as long as you are, I hate to drink alone.....  Cheers to Wayne.
happy birthday sir..
:clapping:Happy Birthday Buddy!!!
Happy b-day bud! If you're in town next week, let me know and I'll buy yah a birthday lunch... I know a place... LMAO! HH
Have a good one Wayne.  All the best to you and your family.
Happy belated Wayne
Happy birthday man. Hope it was a good one.

Happy belated birthday Wayne!! May the next year be filled with joy and happiness for you. You've had enough headache and heartache to last most people a lifetime. Karma will catch up and you have a lot of points in the bank my friend.
Why happy belated birthday,you old cogger.
happy belated wayne.   Art
May you live to be 100 years, with one extra year to repent.
Holy cow ... Bly you are good !!!! ...  Wayne ... Happy 39th bud !!!! You and Jack Benny
it's his birthday......dang   have a great one bud
Wow, going on the teen segment  ! Keep flying pal, age is only a number and only as old as you feel. Heath and family are the main concerns. I'm sure you'll have a great one.  A
Wayne who !!!!  Happy B day Sir !!!!!Have one on me
Happy birthday Wayne I'll crack a cold one in your honor.... cheers
Ditto and many more!!!
Yah.. but feeling 99 sucks Albert! lol  Jon's only off by 10 years...  Thanks Carole!.. and everyone else as well !
Happy Birthday Wayne!
Happy Birthday there young fella! All the very best to you!
Hope it's a great one Wayne.  Happiest of Birthdays to ya.
Happy B-day!!
Happy Birthday Wayne
happy birthday, Wayne !!!
OK, happy birthday Wayne, I hope that as you grow older your sense of humour does not wane either. (groan)
I Gotcha Wayne ... the 'L' word for me this year ... madam J is already acting cagey makin plans-n-stuff  Hope the big 49 turns out to be a really good one for ya !
I'll let ya know Jon... it's not midnight yet...
ROTFL ... jeeze ... that's right ... I forgot !!!!!! This is a month with an "R" in it.. woo hooo
Best wishes for many more to come, hope all works out for ya.
Happy Birthday Wayne !!!  In metric you are only 22.3 years old .
Happy to ya old man! Joe
Have a great day. You won't feel older til the morning after.

From one to another;  With the first light of sun, ...Bless you and yours. When the day is done, ...Bless you and yours. In your smile and in your tears, ...Bless you and yours. Through each day of all your years, ...Bless you and yours.  Happy Birthday Irishfield  Slayer
Happy Birthday
Happy Birthday hon!  39 again eh, you don't look a day over 38  Hope you got something special today (or are gonna tonight   )  Joey
